title: Happy New Year!
description:
The Office Ladies are taking this week off, but we have a special New Years Eve memory shared by the one and only, Creed Bratton. We'll be back January 8th with The Fire.

For more Office Ladies content, head over to Stitcher Premium for the Office Ladies Candy Bag episodes, where Jenna and Angela answer more fan questions. For a free month of Stitcher Premium use code OFFICE.
author: rss@earwolf.com (Earwolf & Jenna Fischer and Angela Kinsey)
